rows.label: tlk42360111_03_msg0001
rows.name: Have you ever read "How Wars Profit Nopon?", mo?

rows.label: tlk42360111_03_msg0002
rows.name:
It analyzes and writes about how much the Nopon
trade guilds would profit if Superbia and Invidia
went to war, mo.

rows.label: tlk42360111_03_msg0003
rows.name:
Since it was written by a Superbian, it's full of
misconceptions about the Nopon tribe, which makes
it interesting in a way, mo.

rows.label: tlk42360111_03_msg0004
rows.name:
It's so hilarious it makes you laugh out loud, so everyone
in the wheelhouse is passing it around, mo.

rows.label: tlk42360111_03_msg0005
rows.name:
Even in tough times, that book can make you
laugh and change your mood, mo.

rows.label: tlk42360111_03_msg0006
rows.name:
If you're interested,
you should buy it at Haskefell Books in
Superbia, mo!
